General.Name: Waystream Holding AB (publ)
General.Description: Waystream Group AB provides routers and switches that are used in the field of high-speed broadband service networks in Sweden. The company offers ASR 8000, MS 8000, and MS 7000, products which provides broadband services to residential and other users. It also provides switches, SFP, and SFP+ modules accessories. In addition, the company offers FTTB switches to deliver voice, video, and data services. Further, it provides technical support, training, and professional services. Additionally, the company offers IPTV monitoring, point-to-point technology, and ZeroTouch automation solutions. The company was formerly known as Waystream Holding AB (publ). Waystream Group AB was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Kista, Sweden.
